  "title": "Recruitment Consultant",
  "description": "<p>Global Role: Maritime, Commodities, Energy, Logistics.</p><p>Angle Recruitment is scaling fast with a reputation that travels across the global maritime world.</p><p>An executive search firm built by seasoned maritime, commodity and energy experts.</p><p>An individual who excels in senior stakeholder engagement is required. Someone skilled in BD, relationship building, and delivering complex global search projects.</p><p><strong>You will:</strong></p><p>- Develop senior client relationships globally across maritime, commodities and energy</p><p>- Lead searches through research, talent mapping, and market insight</p><p>- Grow existing accounts and open new ones</p><p>- Represent a respected brand from Singapore while operating searches globally</p><p><strong>You might be:</strong></p><p>- An experienced executive search professional (Consultant, Manager or Director), or</p><p>- A commercial BD specialist from a sophisticated, non-transactional services environment</p><p><strong>Your existing network isn't important. Your ability to build one is.</strong></p><p><strong>What you get:</strong></p><p>- A seasoned team with deep sector expertise</p><p>- Global exposure. Clients and candidates worldwide</p><p>- Top tier research tools, databases, technology and hardware</p><p>- A collaborative culture. High performance. High reward. High respect</p><p>- Training and support whenever you need it. You succeed, we all succeed</p><p>We expect excellence over abundance. We prioritise exceptional results over volume and take the same approach to developing our people. Discover new ways to raise the bar, set yourself apart, and become one of the best in the industry.</p><p>This formula saw Angle grow into a seven-figure business in its first year. Years two and three have followed the same trajectory.</p><p>Remuneration reflects seniority and performance, with competitive base salaries and industry-leading commissions.</p><p>If you want to join a respected brand known for its performance, people, and distinctive approach... apply. All CVs go directly to Jason Nangle, Managing Director, Global.</p>",
