    "description": "<p><strong>Global Maritime Talent Experts</strong></p>\n<p>Angle Recruitment is a global company that specialises in maritime recruitment and executive search. With our extensive industry expertise and commitment to excellence, we combine traditional values with state-of-the-art technology to deliver exceptional recruitment solutions. Our goal is to establish ourselves as the trusted partner for maritime professionals and organisations seeking top-tier talent. Headquartered in Singapore, one of the world's largest shipping and commodity trading hubs, Angle Recruitment is strategically positioned to serve the global maritime community.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 23S1597</p>",
